latestVersion.termsOfAccess: My intention is to make this data freely available without any restrictions. At this point in time it is restricted until I learn how to use this system and feel comfortable with the process, so just ask if you want to use it.

fields.value: Replication Data for: wa dmhp study 1

dsDescriptionValue.value: This data can be used to replicate the analyses we conducted for our "WA DMHP Study #1". At the time of creating this dataverse, a manuscript had been submitted to SLTB and given a minor revise and resubmit status. We will also publish the R code used to run the analyses for the manuscript.
